{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483890/extras/logo-loopomotive.png?t=1617216507\" /><br><br>Sloths driving trains? An unstoppable train stuck in an endless loop? Cars that mindlessly drive through level crossings? What the h-?<br><br><strong>It doesn't make any sense!</strong><br><br>Welcome to the colorful world of Loopomotive, a small casual game that is entirely free &amp; easy to play. There are no rules and no complex game mechanics, Loopomotive is a wholesome and relaxing game with a simply mechanic, a joyful soundtrack and cute graphics to brighten your day. Spot the curious peeking sloths as you go through 15 unique levels set in a variety of sceneries.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483890/extras/Loopomotive.gif?t=1617216507\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How to play:</h2><br>You drive a train that is stuck in a loop and is unable to fully stop: You can only accelerate, slow down and occasionally use the emergency brake (when it is fully charged).<br><br>Levels in Loopomotive are completed by either running a pre-defined number of loops around the track, surviving until the end of a countdown, or letting a number of cars pass through the tracks safely.<br><br>You lose the level if you hit a vehicle and cause any accidents. Just one accident is too many. (Come on, you don't want to make the sloths sad, do you?)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483890/extras/accidents.gif?t=1617216507\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What you can do:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore 15 levels with unique sceneries, from the underground to the outer space</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find adorable sloths hidden in each level</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock multiple game achievements that add replayability</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pimp your ride and have the coolest train (possibly in the entire world) with unlockable custom skins</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483890/extras/sloth.png?t=1617216507\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Entry-Level","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/a20baade8ead1f4378864d8dac465258e1045a4a.jpg"},{"name":"You're a train wreck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/9e2ee3022ea877083951c863ac800d32c9bd68a8.jpg"},{"name":"Rock Star","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/7ad078678cbc2de075eb0534b4f2b70e53315998.jpg"},{"name":"Bullet Train","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/41109da0113dcad55332d37766d60412ac1716f8.jpg"},{"name":"Light Rail","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/df32683c8d6ed09d7d61d64bfc49987790ed99c8.jpg"},{"name":"Grafitti Artist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/5e15fbd327e0e62cf7748940f06c742d781ff197.jpg"},{"name":"You really are a train wreck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/6188b551e6006d1f31e20d574e8bf3c7c03850cb.jpg"},{"name":"Heart Stopper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/81671b4ba8e460717e11d7c7fbf3158c160a92ec.jpg"},{"name":"Hands-off","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/2fbf940f29d22a291ea1058b50dd7b6cfb897db0.jpg"},{"name":"Catastrophe","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1483890/7ba97a42406293840326b1d65ab2be780553db11.jpg"}],"total":10},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1617216507","background_raw":"